item.title: Aspose.OMR for .NET 19.4 Release Notes
item.description: This page contains release notes information for Aspose.OMR for .NET 19.4 First Public Release of Aspose.OMR for .NET We are pleased to announce the first public release of Aspose.OMR for .NET. It is simple to use API that allows developers to perform OMR operation on images. Aspose.OMR can perform OMR operation on JPEG, PNG, GIF, TIFF, and BMP image files and save the output in CSV format. Please visit the Product Features page for further details and get the chance to download the first release of Aspose.
